data.description: Come see this beautiful 3 bedroom 2 bath home that has a ranch style feel to it and open floor plan in the kitchen and living area. Front living area features a beautiful wood burning stone fireplace.  Home has lots of storage, big closets and the garage has been enclosed for an extra bonus room with endless possibilities. Exterior is brick and stone with a covered front porch. 10 x 10 storage building is also being offered for extra storage. This home sits across the street from the Tioga elementary school, minutes from the new toll road and within minutes to Lake Ray Roberts. Come and see what this great town has to offer! ASSUMABLE 2.75% LOAN for qualified buyer.
